==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: bù àn pái lĭ chū pái

===Etymology===
Literally: to not layout one's ([[wikipedia:Mahjong|Mahjong]]) pieces according to the logic of the (game) pieces

===Idiom===
# think [[outside the box]]; do things in an unconventional way.
